  "2286840": {
    "name": "暗黑穿梭",
    "steam_appid": 2286840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<strong>无数次穿越<br>无数次重生<br>历经沧桑岁月与绝境<br>也要拯救，家人与世界</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8ce765876125a691737ff0af0d739e3a.poster.avif?t=1697738278\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8ce765876125a691737ff0af0d739e3a.webm?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8ce765876125a691737ff0af0d739e3a.mp4?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>跨越量子空间  寻找家园归途</strong><br><br>在垂垂亡矣的世界终末地，你觉醒在量子夹缝之间。在寻找拯救和归属的旅途中，你将结识AI伙伴Darkness；见证一对父女的相互拯救；通过量子之门在历史、未来的无数时空中穿越。你始终坚信，只要自己开启所有时空之门，就能重组空间并寻找到家园归途。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/198b808dad8300295f3266a999f82624.poster.avif?t=1697738278\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/198b808dad8300295f3266a999f82624.webm?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/198b808dad8300295f3266a999f82624.mp4?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>支配时间武器  解锁末日谜题  </strong><br><br>无数次的时空穿越中，你寻找到诸多关于时间的秘密和可信赖的技能，甚至获得了在量子时空生存中最重要的时间控制能力，运用时间操控解开隐秘线索、穿越障碍、使用子弹时间躲避袭击，对量子时空中出没的敌人予以痛击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/6b73738a6c8a03648e6197f5ee8090ca.poster.avif?t=1697738278\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/6b73738a6c8a03648e6197f5ee8090ca.webm?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/6b73738a6c8a03648e6197f5ee8090ca.mp4?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多种武器装备  体验射击乐趣</strong><br><br>在量子空间冒险，更多刺激的射击体验等待着你的挑战！无论你喜欢手持灵活的枪械还是狂暴的重型武器，还是驾驶飞行器进攻防守严密的孤岛，《暗黑穿梭》都能让你找到属于自己的射击乐趣，享受不同的射击快感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/4bb62daeeddbcf92c6e47a78910ede11.poster.avif?t=1697738278\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/4bb62daeeddbcf92c6e47a78910ede11.webm?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/4bb62daeeddbcf92c6e47a78910ede11.mp4?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>烧脑物理解谜  诡谲机关设计</strong><br><br>游戏中遍布逆转乾坤的精巧机关，将量子物理概念与游戏剧情、关卡深入结合，带来全新解谜体验。同时这些机关中也包含了诸多中国传统机关理念设计，将整个游戏组合成为一个超级立体机关。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8b530ae5f66627c88b1c6cdd34112fbb.poster.avif?t=1697738278\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8b530ae5f66627c88b1c6cdd34112fbb.webm?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8b530ae5f66627c88b1c6cdd34112fbb.mp4?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Lowpoly卡通画风   超多彩蛋埋设</strong><br><br>《暗黑穿梭》使用简洁唯美的Lowpoly卡通风格，讲述复杂的末日危途，富有创意的场景设计将为你带来难忘的游戏经历。你可以在游戏中获得多个富有额外能力的装备或装扮，超多的彩蛋埋设相信会为你的时空之旅带来一份乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/d23b662e703b334f31e3eb0e247e83c0.avif?t=1697738278\" width=616 height=198 /></span><br><br><strong>多支线结局  寻找真正归途</strong><br><br>跨时空的逻辑关联&amp;烧脑的解谜探索，共同组成了多重时空穿越谜题。游戏中零散的对话、遗言、密信以及大量的支线剧情，让你的旅途迷雾重重。据说只有从零散信息中勾勒出整个跨度千年的事件全貌，才能解开终极末日谜题，抵达最终的心灵家园。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8de76a86e8cd44f1f5efa199cfc7273d.poster.avif?t=1697738278\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8de76a86e8cd44f1f5efa199cfc7273d.webm?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286840/extras/8de76a86e8cd44f1f5efa199cfc7273d.mp4?t=1697738278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
